Date: Thu, Jun 6, 2013 at 10:47 AM<br>Subject: [ISOC] ANNOUNCEMENT: Internet Society Funds 11 Community-Based Projects that Enhance Internet Environments in Underserved Regions<br>To: &quot;<a href="mailto:isoc-members-announce@...">isoc-members-announce@...</a>&quot; &lt;<a href="mailto:isoc-members-announce@...">isoc-members-announce@...</a>&gt;<br>

